title: BJJ Absolute Class Analysis
text:
This project aims to determine using data what weight a competitor needs to be to have realistic chance of winning the Absolute class at major IBJJF BJJ tournament.

Simple Distribution
From the start graphing a simple distribution we see there is a trend that competitors in the heavier weight classes reach the podium more often.
